{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/technical/medium/2021-08-15_How-to-Debug-Redux-in-React-Native-using-Flipper-d785b46cf7bf/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Yajana Rao"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ced1083b-9ee3-52c8-8f38-cc3d8e2ad551","excerpt":"The flipper-plugin-redux-debugger allows you to read React Native redux logs inside Flipper now:  Install required packages Install  middleware and  in your…","html":"<p>The <a href=\"https://classic.yarnpkg.com/en/package/flipper-plugin-redux-debugger\">flipper-plugin-redux-debugger</a> allows you to read React Native redux logs inside <a href=\"https://fbflipper.com/\">Flipper</a> now:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b5a998990c58948d5f21253c49c48c1b/5a190/1__Zci4wV7eHmxYsr5ebUQfvA.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83783783783784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1  Zci4wV7eHmxYsr5ebUQfvA\"\n        title=\"1  Zci4wV7eHmxYsr5ebUQfvA\"\n        src=\"/static/b5a998990c58948d5f21253c49c48c1b/fcda8/1__Zci4wV7eHmxYsr5ebUQfvA.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b5a998990c58948d5f21253c49c48c1b/12f09/1__Zci4wV7eHmxYsr5ebUQfvA.png 148w,\n/static/b5a998990c58948d5f21253c49c48c1b/e4a3f/1__Zci4wV7eHmxYsr5ebUQfvA.png 295w,\n/static/b5a998990c58948d5f21253c49c48c1b/fcda8/1__Zci4wV7eHmxYsr5ebUQfvA.png 590w,\n/static/b5a998990c58948d5f21253c49c48c1b/5a190/1__Zci4wV7eHmxYsr5ebUQfvA.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4>Install required packages</h4>\n<p>Install <code class=\"language-text\">[redux-flipper](https://github.com/jk-gan/redux-flipper)</code> middleware and <code class=\"language-text\">react-native-flipper</code> in your React Native app:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add --dev redux-flipper react-native-flipper</code></pre></div>\n<p>or</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm i --dev redux-flipper react-native-flipper</code></pre></div>\n<h4>Update pods for ios</h4>\n<p>Install pods for React Native flipper in iOS:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npx pod-install</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">cd ios &amp;&amp; pod install</code></p>\n<h4>Configure redux store</h4>\n<p>Add the middleware into your redux store:</p>\n<p>In case if you are using Redux toolkit:</p>\n<h4>Install Redux debugger plugin</h4>\n<p>Open Flipper desktop client and install <code class=\"language-text\">redux-debugger</code> plugin</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Plugin Manager > Install Plugins > search \"redux-debugger\" > Install redux-debugger</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/e10dec949465485357fb73e6e85f163b/1__xmU__0mAmfBvkMbVNKlVdrg.gif\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h4>Enable redux debugger</h4>\n<p>The <code class=\"language-text\">redux-debugger</code> plugin will be listed in the disabled plugin section. Enable the plugin to get started.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Disabled > Redux Debugger > Enable Plugin</code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"/1aeb0515f33586ec356286c3b78f5580/1__HIXzvdYYHmSKfAac72__Heg.gif\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h4>Start the app to see the logs in Redux debugger</h4>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn android</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">yarn start</code></p>\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: Click on action to see the state</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/59d1f4a7a0ee1578c18ed500884fbf0a/5a190/1__tXVljblKZ1LJwzvjP6x81Q.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83783783783784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1  tXVljblKZ1LJwzvjP6x81Q\"\n        title=\"1  tXVljblKZ1LJwzvjP6x81Q\"\n        src=\"/static/59d1f4a7a0ee1578c18ed500884fbf0a/fcda8/1__tXVljblKZ1LJwzvjP6x81Q.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/59d1f4a7a0ee1578c18ed500884fbf0a/12f09/1__tXVljblKZ1LJwzvjP6x81Q.png 148w,\n/static/59d1f4a7a0ee1578c18ed500884fbf0a/e4a3f/1__tXVljblKZ1LJwzvjP6x81Q.png 295w,\n/static/59d1f4a7a0ee1578c18ed500884fbf0a/fcda8/1__tXVljblKZ1LJwzvjP6x81Q.png 590w,\n/static/59d1f4a7a0ee1578c18ed500884fbf0a/5a190/1__tXVljblKZ1LJwzvjP6x81Q.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to Debug Redux in React Native using Flipper","date":"August 15, 2021","description":"The flipper-plugin-redux-debugger allows you to read React Native redux logs inside Flipper now:"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/technical/medium/2021-08-15_How-to-Debug-Redux-in-React-Native-using-Flipper-d785b46cf7bf/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/queries/2020-08-01-integrate-react-native-web-to-existing-application/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"How to Integrate react-native-web in an existing react native application"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/technical/medium/2021-08-22_How-to-build-Responsive-React-Native-Components-using-Restyle-7eb2742538a5/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"How to build Responsive React Native Components using Restyle"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1105976633","1205699325","1246554614","2841359383","3336116537"]}